{"id": "mii1665702640966", "title": "Tab Offset (TabOffset)", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Development Object and Property Reference", "Development Object Properties", "Presentation Properties", "FRM Widget Properties for Fields", "Tab Offset (TabOffset)"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mii1665702640966.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Tab Offset (TabOffset)</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Tab Height (TabHeight) \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Tab Height (TabHeight) \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jly1665702640894.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   Tab Space (TabSpace) \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   Tab Space (TabSpace) \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzs1665702641037.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/mii1665702640966.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/mii1665702640966.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/mii1665702640966.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mii1665702640966.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mii1665702640966.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mii1665702640966.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mii1665702640966\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                              \n Tab Offset (TabOffset) \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Number of character cells (or pixels) that the edge of the tab strip is separated from edges of the widget. Default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> (no offset).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107696e1_d107697e1_d107698e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TabOffset<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Cells</var> |\n            <var class=\"keyword varname\">Pixels</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">px</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No tab offset.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Cells</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Offset as number of character cells.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Pixels</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">px</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12692e1_d12693e1_d12694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Offset as number of pixels.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_cty_mbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e158\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mii1665702640966__table_d12695e1_d12696e1_d12697e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_uqp_4bz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e218\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107705e1_d107706e1_d107707e1\">The tab offset is in character cells, unless the\n            number is followed by <code class=\"ph codeph\">px</code>, in which case the offset is in pixels.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107708e1_d107709e1_d107710e1\">If TabsAlignment is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">right</code>,\n            and the total width of all the tabs does not exceed the width of the widget, the offset\n            is calculated from the right edge of the widget. IN all other cases the offset is\n            calculated from the left edge.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107711e1_d107712e1_d107713e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Justify</span> property is\n            set, it overrides <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Offset</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_w2l_pbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e245\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107717e1_d107718e1_d107719e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mii1665702640966__pre_fw5_qbz_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"taboffset=10px\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_m3x_qbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e278\">Example: Left Tab Offset</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107723e1_d107724e1_d107725e1\">The following ProcScript sets the offset to 3\n            character cells. For clarity, a border is displayed by setting the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> property to <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mii1665702640966__pre_y1q_tbz_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vProperties = \"\" ; string variable to contain widget properties\n\n; Create list of properties\nputitem/id vProperties,\"taboffset\",\"3\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"frame\",\"T\"\n\n;Assign propoperties list to field TAB\n$fieldproperties(TAB) = vProperties</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107726e1_d107727e1_d107728e1\">By default, tabs in the tab strip are left aligned,\n            so the offset is from the left.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"mii1665702640966__fig_d107729e1_d107730e1_d107731e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Left Offset</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"mii1665702640966__image_s2w_5bz_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/taboffset_left3.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_z3k_vbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e311\">Example: Right Tab Offset</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mii1665702640966__p_d107738e1_d107739e1_d107740e1\">The following ProcScript sets the TabOffset to 3\n            character cells and TabsAlignment to <code class=\"ph codeph\">right</code>. For clarity, a border is\n            displayed by setting the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> property to\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"mii1665702640966__fig_d107741e1_d107742e1_d107743e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Right Offset</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"mii1665702640966__image_wcs_xbz_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/taboffset_right3.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mii1665702640966__section_lhf_ybz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d241157e341\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wda1665702641324.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tabs Alignment (TabsAlignment)</a><p>The Tabs Alignment widget property determines how tabs are aligned in a horizontal strip. Default is Left.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nym1665702640684.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Justified (Justify)</a><p>Justifies the tabs so that they occupy the full width of the tab widget. Default is False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Offset (TabOffset) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tab Offset (TabOffset) Number of character cells (or pixels) that the edge of the tab strip is separated from edges of the widget. Default is 0 (no offset). \" TabOffset = Cells | Pixels px \" Value Description 0 No tab offset. Cells Offset as number of character cells. Pixels px Offset as number of pixels. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Description The tab offset is in character cells, unless the number is followed by px , in which case the offset is in pixels. If TabsAlignment is set to right , and the total width of all the tabs does not exceed the width of the widget, the offset is calculated from the right edge of the widget. IN all other cases the offset is calculated from the left edge. If the Justify property is set, it overrides Tab Offset . Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"taboffset=10px\" Copy Example: Left Tab Offset The following ProcScript sets the offset to 3 character cells. For clarity, a border is displayed by setting the Frame property to true . vProperties = \"\" ; string variable to contain widget properties ; Create list of properties putitem/id vProperties,\"taboffset\",\"3\" putitem/id vProperties,\"frame\",\"T\" ;Assign propoperties list to field TAB $fieldproperties(TAB) = vProperties Copy By default, tabs in the tab strip are left aligned, so the offset is from the left. Figure 1. Left Offset Example: Right Tab Offset The following ProcScript sets the TabOffset to 3 character cells and TabsAlignment to right . For clarity, a border is displayed by setting the Frame property to true . Figure 2. Right Offset Applies To utabex (TabEx) Related Links Tabs Alignment (TabsAlignment) The Tabs Alignment widget property determines how tabs are aligned in a horizontal strip. Default is Left. Justified (Justify) Justifies the tabs so that they occupy the full width of the tab widget. Default is False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}